                xml:lang="en-us">
    <title>Prerequisites</title>
    <conbody>
        <section>
            <p>For installing the Monitoring Service, a machine is required with:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <p>Docker 1.12. For details, refer to the <xref
                        format="html"
                        href="https://docs.docker.com/v1.12/"
                        scope="external">
                        <u><i>Docker documentation</i></u></xref>.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>Docker Compose 1.14. For details, refer to the <xref format="html"
                            href="https://docs.docker.com/v1.12/compose/overview/" scope="external">
                            <u><i>Docker Compose documentation</i></u></xref>. </p>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </conbody>
</concept>
